### POST /query

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5220

### Housing (default)
POST {{baseUrl}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Should I live at 14 Clerkenwell Road?"
}

### Routing
POST {{baseUrl}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Get me home",
  "location": { "lat": 51.5308, "lng": -0.1238 }
}

### Activity
POST {{baseUrl}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "I'm free for 3 hours",
  "location": { "lat": 51.5231, "lng": -0.0789 }
}
